scripts
=======

This directory includes various scripts to submit array & batch jobs
to a cluster and do pre- & post-processing of simulation results for
the ECR study of next-generation optical access networks.

The following is the explanation of typical workflow.

1. Run simulations

Use 'arrayrun.sh' script to submit a batch job to cluster (Grid
Engine) as in the following example:

qsub -t 1:50 -o directoryForStandardOutput -j yes arrayrun.sh iniFile configuration


2. Analyze results
